to launch to heroku
--

1) heroku create [name of the app]
2) go to package.json, under script 

"scripts": {
    "start" : "node src/app.js"
},

3) go to main application with epxress, include 

const port = process.env.PORT || 3000 

4)

TO PUSH TO HEROKU, must push to git first

>git push

then to push to heroku

> git push heroku master